## Implementation Checklist

When implementing natural conversation flow:

- [ ] **Extract conversation context** from message history
- [ ] **Track known parameters** across conversation turns
- [ ] **Build contextual responses** that reference known information
- [ ] **Generate realistic suggestions** with actual amounts and tokens
- [ ] **Write suggestions in user voice** ("I want to..." not "Please specify...")
- [ ] **Avoid placeholder text** like [amount], [token], [strategy]
- [ ] **Test conversation continuity** with multi-turn scenarios
- [ ] **Measure conversation efficiency** (exchanges to completion)
- [ ] **Validate context retention** (responses reference previous messages)

